<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
  		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100|Ubuntu" rel="stylesheet">	
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
		<title>To Do List</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles/style.css" type="text/css">
		<script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/handlebars.js/4.0.5/handlebars.min.js"></script>
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
		<script src="./scripts/app.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
	  <div class="container">
	    <h1 class="text-center">To Do List</h1>
	    <h4>Gurrrlll, what you doing walking about without a to do list?? How do you expect yourself to get anything done??? Start writing it all down!</h4>
	    <div class="row">
	      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
	        <form class="form-inline" id="newToDoForm">
	          <div class="form-group">
	            <label for="title">Task:</label><br />
	            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="task" id="taskInput" placeholder="I need to do...">
	          </div>
	          <div class="form-group">
	            <label for="title">How To Accomplish:</label><br />
	            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="description" placeholder="How do you do that?">
	          </div>
	          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default create">Tack that on the list!</button>
	        </form>
	        <div id='toDoTarget'>
	        </div>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	</body>
</html>